	<p>
		In this text, you will encounter many different methods for solving differential equations. The method that you apply will be based on some aspect or property of a differential equation. So, it makes sense to separate differential equations into groups that have properties in common. This grouping process is known as <em>classification</em> and it will be one of the first things we consider before discussing a new technique for solving a differential equation.
	</p>

